 IP: 173.233.80.101) or New York City (test IP: 108.60.141.3). They have been around for a while \u2014 since 2003 according to their <a href=\"http://hudsonvalleyhost.com/aboutus.html\">About page</a>, and domain registered in 2004. They were reselling Virpus when they <a href=\"/blog/hudsonvalleyhost-5-70-384mb-openvz-vps/\">first got featured here</a>, but has since moved on and have their own VPS reseller program. It has a few good reviews <a href=\"/blog/hudson-valley-host-4-50-256mb-openvz-vps/\">last time the same deal got posted here</a> (although it was a little bit cheaper back then).</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fhudson-valley-host-4-95-256mb-openvz-vps-in-new-york%2F&amp;t=Hudson%20Valley%20Host%20-%20%244.95%20256MB%20OpenVZ%20VPS%20in%20New%20York\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Hudson%20Valley%20Host%20-%20%244.95%20256MB%20OpenVZ%20VPS%20in%20New%20York&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fhudson-valley-host-4-95-256mb-openvz-vps-in-new-york%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-twitter dpsp-no-label\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?url=htt